message.content:
Tēnā koe! Kei te whakapau kaha ahau ki te āwhina i a koe. Ko te whakararuraru i ngā kōrero hē mō tētahi kaitono tōrangapū, he kaupapa whakahirahira. Ka whakararuraru ngā whakapuaki o ngā kōrero whakapau kaha ana i te whakaputanga o te pānui, ā, ka whakapau kaha hoki i te whakaputanga whakapau kaha o te kaitono. 

Hei te whakapau kaha i a koe, me whakararuraru i ngā āhuatanga whakawhitiwhiti kōrero, whakapuakina ngā whakapuaki i te tika me te whakamārama hoki i ngā āhuatanga whakatika. Ka whakararuraru hoki i ngā whakapuaki o ngā whakapuaki whakatika, me whakamārama ki te kaitono i te āhuatanga o te hē, ā, me whakararuraru hoki i ngā whakapuaki o ngā whakapuaki whakamārama, kia whakamārama ai ki te kaitono te whakamārama o te whakaputanga. 

Ka whakararuru ake i te kaitono, me pātai i a rātou he whakamāramatanga anō rātou e hiahia ana, ka whakapau kaha i a rātou ki te whakapuaki i ngā whakapuaki whakamārama me ngā whakapuaki whakapuakina. Ka whakararuru rātou ki te whakapuaki i ngā āhuatanga o ngā whakaputanga, me whakamārama hoki ki a rātou i te āhuatanga o te hē me ngā whakatikat
